Template: llm-systems-agent/manager-url
Type: string
Description: Manager URL:
 URL of the LLM Systems Manager this agent reports to, e.g.
 http://192.0.2.10:5000. Leave blank to set it later in
 /opt/llm-systems-agent/agent_config.yaml.

Template: llm-systems-agent/alarm-engine-url
Type: string
Description: Alarm engine URL:
 Leave blank to derive it from the manager host (port 8081).
